---
title: Smart Jalapeño and Feta Chicken Fritters with Charred Corn Salad and Cilantro Aioli
description: These delightful chicken fritters get a kiss of heat from jalapeños , a hit of smokiness from charred corn and a touch of saltiness from feta. You'll pan-fry them to golden perfection, then serve them alongside a fresh salad to create a gorgeous plate!

